title: Black Mirror Season 5 Review
description:
What happens when two best friends have sex in a video game? What about phone addiction and guilt grief? How bad is fake pop punk? Dr. Kirk Honda and Humberto talk about the newest Black Mirror episodes.

The Psychology In Seattle Podcast.
June 12, 2019.
